{"tid":1221331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記得將你喺場上習得嘅技能配俾同路人","createTime":"2019-06-14T07:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T15:31:38.000Z","uid":33495,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6da2e8016ea1300fd7cc38e29082d06794f9eb63","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:35:55.000Z","msg":"經過呢幾日，相信好多朋都已經脫離咗新手村<br />\n知道邊度要放哨、邊度要收風、點樣先唔會進退失據<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺呢啲之前其實仲有好多簡單啲嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如邊啲口罩眼鏡先有用<br />\n邊啲遮有用邊啲冇用<br />\n生理鹽水要點用<br />\n水源要放喺邊先方便前線去救熄催淚彈<br />\n場地地形嘅安全點、 危險位置<br />\n有咩捷徑搬運、走佬快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n越簡單嘅知識越重要，越要分享俾同路人<br />\n佢唔敢上，好可能係因為新手唔識<br />\n唔識嘅人都提下佢，呢啲時間冇人會reject你<br />\n攞出嚟分享，配埋技能點比佢<br />\n越多人有信心，我哋支援嘅人越多，勝算越大<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有時間休息、調整心態。我哋要贏埋佢！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1b644cbb8b5043e6c4355608fab8415433860d","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b88086b838cf36a72df550469c9835382d797b1","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5908073eccf03a4102a60e91519395096ca101a5","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2e4d6e72dec2507069ddbfaa47c3af0b5194e6","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59fb9a6db8ad863d29fa5a16f104b88e3de42fd2","tid":1221331,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8c8ab9e5cc1dc64e240f5b4be842ebf187a2730","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T07:57:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaa3b74aa13e7e5948e15c66472c36b43e90a07e","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c37ce00f65854d13f237aa524f3c4f930578df1","tid":1221331,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}